<subSubSection pageId="41" pageNumber="435" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="41.[120,1326,729,1472]" pageId="41" pageNumber="435">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[122,477,1320,1353]" pageId="41" pageNumber="435">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The [UCN Red List. Celaque Broad-clawed Shrews are found in the Celaque National Park and seem to have a restricted distribution, but additional research is needed.
</paragraph>
